<tmimprep><title>Technical Manual Improvement Report Preparation</title>
<subpara1><title>Improvement Reports</title><para>Recommendations
for improvements to this technical order shall be submitted on AFTO
Form 22, Technical Manual (TM) Change Recommendation and Reply. Complete
AFTO Form 22 in accordance with TO 00-5-1.</para>
</subpara1>
</tmimprep>
